      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand, something in the tier of Patek Philippe or maybe even a bit more exclusive. we need to nail the target demographic for our global launch. can you help me define the \"ideal consumer\" profile? i need more than just income levels—i want to understand their lifestyle, their cultural background, and even their ethnicity so we can make sure our imagery and branding really resonate with the right people. who is this person?",
